==Arabic==
===Etymology 1===
A contraction of {{ARchar|[[ان|إن]]}} + {{ARchar|[[لا]]}} (’in+lā), "if not".

====Preposition====
'''{{ARchar|إلا}}''' (’illā)

# [[except]], [[save]]
# [[unless]], if not
#''(after negation)'' [[only]], [[but]], not [[until]]

===Etymology 2===
A contraction of {{ARchar|[[ان|أن]]}} + {{ARchar|[[لا]]}} (’an+lā), "that not".

====Conjunction====
'''{{ARchar|ألا}}''' (’allā)

# [[lest]]
# that...not
# in order that...not
# so as not to

===Etymology 3===
A contraction of {{ARchar|[[ا]]}} + {{ARchar|[[ما]]}} (’a+mā), "interrogative what".

====Particle====
'''{{ARchar|الا}}''' (’alā)

# [[verily]], [[truly]], [[indeed]], oh yes!

===Etymology 4===
From the root {{ARchar|[[الو]]}}, to neglect to do.

====Verb I====
'''{{ARchar|الا}}''' (’alā)

# to [[neglect]] to do, to [[fail]] to do, not to do
# to [[desist]], to [[refrain]]

